s such as which prevail within the Local\nBubble and its walls, and the opposite is true for cooler/shielded regions\nbeyond the confines of the Local Bubble, we unexpectedly also detect DIB\ncloudlets inside of the Local Bubble. These results reveal new insight into the\nstructure of the Local Bubble, as well as helping constrain our understanding\nof the carriers of the DIBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2015 15:03:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-24"}
